### Get all users (Requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a specific user by ID (Requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new user (Requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie",
